Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Excellent access to major road arterials

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to present for lease 65 Translink Drive, Keilor Park.

This outstanding building is strategically located just off Keilor Park Drive and within minutes of the Calder Freeway on-ramp, providing excellent access to all major road arterial.

Key features include:
+ Modern Office/Warehouse on Prominent Corner Location with Dual Access
+ Total building area of 1,366sqm*
+ Warehouse area of 998sqm*
+ Corporate Two (2) level office area of 368sqm*
+ 2 x Container Height RSDs
+ High clearance and clearspan warehouse
+ Workstations and Pallet Racking*
+ Dumbwaiter Lift (Capacity 50kg)
+ Full amenities including lunchroom with kitchenette and male and female bathrooms
+ 16 car spaces within secured yard
+ Available April 2017 or earlier by arrangement

Please contact the marketing agents for inspection and further information.

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to exclusively present 75 Harrick Road, Keilor Park, for lease, available now.

This well-appointed corporate facility of 3,316sqm*, formerly occupied by Porsche, comes with a large 2,837sqm* fully sprinklered warehouse, 479sqm* two-level open plan office space and is sure to appeal to companies looking for their next HQ.

Located within the highly sought-after industrial suburb of Keilor Park, this property offers great access to Melbourne International Airport, M80 Western Ring Road as well as Calder and Tullamarine Freeways.

Property Features Include:
+ Total building area: 3,316sqm*
+ Office areas: 479sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 2,837sqm*
+ Awning over loading
+ Three (3) container height roller doors
+ Drive through capability
+ Three phase power
+ Fully sprinklered warehouse
+ Large rear hardstand 
+ Dual entrance points
+ Multiple car spaces 
+ Great amenity
+ Available now

For further details on this property or your commercial property needs, please contact the marketing agents Jake George on 0421 221 019 or Joe Brzezek on 0481 167 343.
